title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Aug 30 2022

description:
The liberal media is trying to suppress GOP turnout, while energizing the Democrat base. It is imperative that the Republicans win the House and Senate. Pennsylvania Democrat John Fetterman: I’m against voter ID because poor people and "people of color" are "less likely to have their ID." Why is the media ignoring Fetterman's massive stroke? Mollie Hemingway: Biden’s "semi-fascism" comments "more hateful than the worst thing Trump ever said." With 70 days until the midterm election, Clay and Buck discuss what’s at stake. With the upcoming football season, what are the other entertainment choices for C&B?
